text: Terrenc Griemink (born 6 March 1997) is a Dutch korfball player. He is a member of KV Groen Geel and the Netherlands national korfball team. Griemink became a member of the national team in July 2021. With the national team he won the gold medal at the 2022 World Games in Birmingham, Alabama. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch korfball players
